      <div class="cr-tags">
        <span class="cr-tag cr-tag-orange">30-day creative challenge</span>
        <span class="cr-tag cr-tag-dark">March 22 – April 12, 2026</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="cr-title"><span class="wavy">Mess Is Medicine</span></h1>
      <p class="cr-tagline">where perfectionism goes to die</p>
      <p class="cr-outcome">Write every day for 30 days… even if it's just 2 minutes. You'll leave with:</p>
      <ul class="cr-leaves">
        <li>more material than you wrote all year</li>
        <li>a daily creative habit that actually sticks</li>
        <li>the freedom to stop curating yourself</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="cr-medicine-line">Perfection is boring. Mess is medicine.</p>
      <svg class="doodle-arrow cr-doodle-cta" width="52" height="38" viewBox="0 0 52 38" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M6 5 C 14 4, 38 16, 44 30" stroke="#d64063" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <path d="M37 27 L44 30 L40 22" stroke="#d64063" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
      <a class="btn btn-primary cr-btn-centered" href="https://buy.stripe.com/14A3cwbULgLleQxceP3Je01" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join Now · $250</a>
      <p class="trust-bar">🔒 Secure checkout via Stripe &nbsp;·&nbsp; Live calls Sundays 2pm PT &nbsp;·&nbsp; Spots capped at 30</p>
